Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}プロセカアフタートーク、ColorsofPureSense編。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}ProSeka AfterTalk: Colors of Pure Sense edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}はい、え、こんばんは。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Hello, everyone! Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}25時ナイトコードで宵崎奏役の鈴木みのりです。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'm Minori Suzuki, the voice of Ena Shinonome from Nightcord at 25:00."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:13.18,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、このプロセカアフタートークは皆さんから頂いたお頼りを紹介しながらイベントを振り返る番組となっております。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}ProSeka AfterTalk is a program where we look back on the event while reading the messages you've sent in."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:16.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}今回はColorsofPureSense編でございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Today, we're covering the Colors of Pure Sense event."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.24,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}皆さんストーリーはお楽しみいただけましたでしょうか?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Did you all enjoy the story?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.08,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:25.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}感謝祭とか、あの、劇場版の舞台挨拶とかね、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Between the Fan Festa and the movie's stage greetings,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:30.52,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}リアルのキャストが出る方のイベントも忙しい中すぐ、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}it's been a busy time for the cast with all the live events."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:35.14,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、この25のイベント、えなのお話のイベントがやってきてね、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And right in the middle of that, we got this Niigo event focused on Ena's story."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:39.06,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、結構わーってなんかなってたと思うですけれども、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'm sure everyone's heads were spinning with all the news,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:42.52,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}楽しんでいただけてたなら幸いでございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but I hope you've been enjoying it all."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:49.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、事前にプロセカ公式Discordとメールにてアフタートークへのお頼りを募集しておりました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}We previously asked for messages for this AfterTalk via the official ProSeka Discord and email."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、皆さんお頼りありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you all for writing in!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:56.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}なんか全部こっそりスタッフさんに見せて欲しいぐらいね、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I honestly wish the staff would let me sneak a peek at every single one,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.86,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ちょっと皆さんの感想気になるんですけれども。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}because I'm so curious about your thoughts."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:03.56,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}で、こちらの頂いたお頼りを番組内でご紹介させて頂きますので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'll be sharing some of those messages during the show,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:04.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}お楽しみに。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:11.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}また、イベントやこの放送の感想をハッシュタグプロセカアフタートークでポストしてください。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Also, please post your impressions of the event or this stream using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}YouTubeのチャットも見ているので気になる方は、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'm also keeping an eye on the YouTube chat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.89,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}あ、気になるコメントはどんどん拾っていきます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so I'll be picking up comments that catch my eye."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:18.79,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}はい。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:19.51,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}え、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}いいストーリーでしたとかね、こん25とかもね、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I see comments like "It was a great story" and "Kon-Niigo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:24.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ありますね。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}こん25でございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Kon-Niigo to you too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:30.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、そして、今日はえ、22時からね、アフターライブもありますし、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And today, we have the AfterLive starting at 10:00 PM,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.18,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}22時5分に今回のイベントの3{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and at 10:05 PM, the 3DMV for this event"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:40.12,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}DMVが公開されるので、それをみんなと一緒に見ていきたいと思っております。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}will be released, so I want to watch that together with all of you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.56,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}なので、ちょっと時間遵守でやっていきたいんですけれども。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So, I'll try to keep us on schedule."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:48.34,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}だけれどもストーリー動画もちょっと長めに見ていきたいと思いますので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}That said, I want to spend a good amount of time watching the story clips."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:53.82,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}いつもよりね、ちょっと私がわがまま言いまして、ちょっとストーリー長めになっておりますので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I was a bit selfish and asked to make the story segment longer than usual,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:56.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、是非是非ご覧いただければなと思います。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so I hope you'll enjoy watching it with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:03.86,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}それでは早速今回のColorsofPureSenseのストーリーについてお話、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Now then, let's start talking about the story"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、できればと思います。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}for Colors of Pure Sense."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}皆さん今回のストーリーはいかがでしたでしょうか?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}What did you all think of the story this time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:14.00,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ねえ、お頼りを紹介しながら一緒にストーリー振り返っていきましょう。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Let's look back on it together while reading your messages."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:19.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}私このプロセカアフタートークリニューアルされて初めてなんですよ。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Actually, this is my first time doing ProSeka AfterTalk since the renewal."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.96,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}1年ぶりぐらいで、1年前は多分リニューアル前なので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's been about a year, and back then it was the old format,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:31.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}このみんなのお頼りからの言葉を紡ぐみたいなのは初めてなのでちょっと嬉しいですね。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so I'm really happy to be doing this new style where I build the conversation around your messages."
Comment: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,=== Corner: Fan Letter Corner ===
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.12,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、アメリアタイムさんからのお頼りでございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Here's a message from Amelia Time."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.74,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、初めて感想送ります。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"This is my first time sending in my thoughts.""
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:43.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}私が印象に残ったシーンは絵名が自撮りのアカウントを消すところのシーンです。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"The scene that left the biggest impression on me was when Ena deleted her selfie account."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:50.22,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}絵と向き合うことから逃げてしまう絵名が向き合おうと決意したところに成長を感じました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I felt so much growth in her when she decided to stop running away and finally face her art."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:55.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}また、私も絵名と同じように自分と向き合うことが怖くて逃げていましたが、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I've also been running away because I was scared to face myself, just like Ena,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:13:00.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}絵名の前向きな姿に背中を押された気がして自分も頑張ろうと思いました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but seeing her move forward gave me a push, and now I want to try my best too.""
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:07.12,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、鈴木さんはえ、絵名にどんな思いを乗せて今回演じられましたか?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"Suzuki-san, what kind of feelings did you put into your performance of Ena this time?""
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.50,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ということでありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you for that wonderful message."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}え、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:17.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}アメリアタイムさんね、素敵なお頼り頂きましたけれどもそうですね、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Amelia Time-san, that was a lovely letter. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:26.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}また後ほどストーリーを見ながらもお話しできたらなって思うんですけれども今回の絵名、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'll talk more about this while we watch the story later, but regarding Ena in this event,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:31.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あとは最近の25の楽曲を歌う時に絵名として意識していた、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and what I've been keeping in mind when singing Niigo's recent songs as Ena...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:49.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}キャストとして意識していた部分っていうのはもう昔の絵名に戻らないぞっていうのはこう個人的に意識していてやっぱその速度は{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}As her voice actress, I've personally made a conscious effort to show that she's never going back to her old self. Even if the pace is slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:14:04.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ゆっくりながらも絵名もちょっとずつちょっとずつ前に進んでいるからこそ25はやっぱりどうしても楽曲のタイプ的にも後ろ向きになりがちな言葉だったりとか、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Ena is moving forward bit by bit. Because of the nature of Niigo's music, the lyrics and atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}えっと楽曲の雰囲気があったりするものもあるんですけれども、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}tend to lean toward being quite negative or gloomy at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:16.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そこに引っ張られすぎずに、そしてま、もしかしたらちょっとこう波だのニュアンスを含んでいたりとか、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I try not to let myself get pulled too far into that. Honestly, it might be easier to include
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:24.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}マイナスなニュアンスを含んだ方が、ま、正直歌としてセリフとして皆さんの耳におってなったりとかあの、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}nuances of tears or negativity to make a line or a song really grab the listeners' attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:28.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}聞きたいなって、なんかここのフレーズいいなって思って目に、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}or to make them think, "Oh, I love this phrase."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:33.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}耳に届、止まるものもすごくあるとは思うんですけど、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I know those are the things that really stick in people's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:38.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}でもそれは鈴木がこう見せたいっていうあの、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But if I did that, it would just be my own desire for validation as a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:48.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}承認欲求でしかないので、ちゃんと絵名がちょっとずつでも前を向いているんだぞっていうのを歌とセリフに乗せよう。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I want to make sure Ena's songs and lines convey that she's looking forward, even if it's just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:56.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}だから同じ言葉でもちゃんと前に進んでるっていうのをこう感じてもらえるようにあの、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So even with the same words, I try to make sure you can feel her progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:15:06.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}意識して、で、その前向き度合いもストーリーを踏まえてちょっとずつ増やしていってっていうね、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I've been gradually increasing that sense of positivity based on the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:11.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}なんかそういうのをこう意識してえ、今回演じさせて頂きました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}That's what I focused on while performing her this time."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}で、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:23.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そうですね、今回もですし、最近の楽曲もなんかそこまで物事に対してなんか自分が思ってたよりも世の中ってあったかいし、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}not just this time, but in recent songs too, I think Ena has realized that the world is warmer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:28.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}周りの人って自分を助けてくれるんだっていうことをちゃんと分かっている絵名だと思うので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and people are more willing to help than she originally thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.64,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}それは意識してやらせて頂きました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I kept that in mind during the recording."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}では、え、続いてですね、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.26,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、もう1つお頼りご紹介させて頂きます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'd like to read another letter."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:43.06,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}すだちうどんさんからのお頼りでございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}This one is from Sudachi Udon-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}みのりさんこんばんは。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"Good evening, Minori-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}こんばんは。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.94,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、ColorsofPureSense見させて頂きました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"I read the Colors of Pure Sense story.""
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:50.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:58.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}私が印象に残ったのは第7話の絵名が絵を描くことが楽しくて仕方なくて気持ちが高揚していくシーンです。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"What left an impression on me was the scene in Episode 7 where Ena gets so excited because she's having so much fun drawing.""
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:06.34,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、他者評価、かっこ自撮りなど、でしか自己肯定感を上げられなかった絵名がやっと私は私のままでいい、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"Ena used to only get self-validation from others, like through her selfies, but she finally realized she's fine just as she is.""
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:14.46,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}私の世界や表現は私の思うまま自由でいいんだって気づき絵名の世界がだんだんカラフルに彩られ、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"She realized her world and expression can be as free as she wants. Her world gradually became more colorful,""
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:21.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}絵を描くの楽しいって目の輝きもどんどんキラキラしていく様がみのりさんの声からひしひしと伝わり、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"and the way her eyes sparkled as she enjoyed drawing really came through in your voice, Minori-san.""
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}涙が出ました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"It actually brought me to tears.""
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:30.30,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}夢のために、絵のために諦めない覚悟を決めた絵名をこれからも見守り応援していきたいと思います。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"I want to keep watching over and supporting Ena as she resolves to never give up on her art and her dreams.""
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:34.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}みのりさん、絵名の心の色お、すごい素敵な文章ですね。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"Minori-san, thank you for showing us the colors of Ena's heart so vividly through your voice." What a lovely message."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:39.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}声の表現でこんなにも鮮やかに見せてくれて本当にありがとうございました。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you so much for those kind words."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ということで、ありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I really appreciate it."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.64,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}こちらこそ、受け取ってくださってありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}No, thank YOU for receiving it that way."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:53.02,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}やっぱりいつも思うのはね、なんかこう絵名の心が届いたらいいなって思うので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I always hope that Ena's heart and feelings reach all of you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:58.70,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}もちろんやっぱりゲームのキャラクターであってあの、2次元というものではあるんですけど、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Of course, she's a game character and a 2D creation,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.38,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}でもちゃんと絵名は生きていて、絵名はあの、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but Ena is truly alive to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:06.86,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}未来、絵名の未来なんてまだまだ誰にも分からないことなので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Nobody knows what her future holds yet,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.48,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}なんかそういうなんでしょうね。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and that's why..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:16.96,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ちゃんとその生のものを届けられたらいいなと思っているので嬉しい感想、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I want to deliver something that feels real and raw, so I'm happy to hear your thoughts."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.24,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ありがとうございます。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.51,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}はい。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:29.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ということでま、色々話したいので、ストーリー見ながらちょっと気を抜いて今ここで喋りすぎるとあの、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I have so much more I want to talk about while we watch the story, and if I'm not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あっという間に5分になっちゃうので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}five minutes will pass in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.36,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}サクサクといきたいと思います。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So let's keep things moving along!"
Comment: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,=== Corner: Story Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:39.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}今回も私が個人的に語りたいシーンをピックアップしましたので、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I've picked out a few scenes I personally want to talk about,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}一緒に見ていきましょう。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so let's watch them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}今日は私がわがまま言いまして、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I was actually a bit selfish today—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:47.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}わがまま言いましたって言うとめっちゃ首振ってくれるんですけど、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}the staff are shaking their heads at me saying I was selfish, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.03,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}スタッフさん。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}well, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:48.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あの、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I really had a hard time choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}悩んだんですよ。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I felt like saying, "Let's just watch episodes 1 through 8 together!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:54.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんならもう1話から8話一緒に見ましょうぐらいの勢いではあるんですが、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But for now, we're going to take a look at episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:18:00.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}え、7話と8話を見ていきたいと思います。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Since this is AfterTalk, I'm going to be doing a lot of talking."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.85,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}これはアフタートークでトークなんでね 、ちょっとみのりがいろいろ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So, Minori—that's me—"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、みのりね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'll be chatting quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの 、私ね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}If I get too noisy for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:04.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}が喋るからうるさい方は 、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I hope you'll bear with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ちゃんとゲームの方でまた改めて見ていただければなと思いますよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I hope you'll all take another look at the story in the game itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:14.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:14.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}では早速行きましょう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Let's jump right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:15.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}7話と8話です{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Here are episodes 7 and 8."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}どうぞ 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:18.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}すごいなあ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:26.86,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:27.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}お父さんの絵{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Dad's painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:29.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんだかキラキラしてて{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's so sparkly and bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:33.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}私が見てるのと同じ世界じゃないみたい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's like it's not even the same world I'm looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:38.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}どうしてこんな絵が描けるだろう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}How can he paint like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:44.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:48.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}どうした{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:53.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:53.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あのね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Hey, Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:56.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんで今赤塗ったの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}why did you just use red?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}この葉っぱ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}This leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:01.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}赤いところないのに{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}it doesn't have any red on it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:04.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そうだな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}その方がいいと思ったんだ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I just thought it would look better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:11.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}お父さんにはそう見えてるの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Is that how it looks to you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:18.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そうじゃない{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}いや{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}違わないのかもしれないな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}maybe it's not that different after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:27.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ん ?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}よくわかんない{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:33.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:33.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}目に見える色は違うかもしれないが{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}The colors I see with my eyes might be different,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:38.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}こう描きたいと思ったんだ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but this is how I wanted to paint it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:41.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}描きたい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}How you wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}それでいいの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:45.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}?{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:46.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}全然違う色なのに{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Even though the color is totally different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:49.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ああ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:51.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}絵は自由だ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Art is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}自分だけの世界だからな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's a world all your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}だから{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:57.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}自分の好きなように描けばいい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}you should paint it however you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:19:59.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ああ 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}自分だけの世界{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}A world all your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:05.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}じゃあ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:07.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}この絵はお父さんの世界なのかな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}is this painting your world, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:13.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}すっごく綺麗で{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's so beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:19.13,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}不思議{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:20.86,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}次はどんな色に塗るのかな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I wonder what color you'll use next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あの枝に止まってる鳥はどんな風になるんだろう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I wonder what that bird on the branch will look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:28.79,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 は{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:34.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Comment: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:34.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あの頃{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.15,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}絵を描くお父さんの手が{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}my father's hands as he painted
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:44.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんだか魔法みたいに見えたっけ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}seemed almost like magic to me.
