Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.92,0:34:43.55,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}最後の方は{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}is because of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.55,0:34:44.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}A lot has happened between them,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.62,0:34:45.31,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}思いながら{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and there were times
