Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.54,0:35:01.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}すごく 、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}that those feelings were still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.44,0:26:31.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}憧れているのは 、多分{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I also got to voice
