Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.92,0:26:43.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}だからこそ 、幼少期のエナも{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I acted with the image of her talking to someone like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.90,0:26:44.53,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、演じさせていただいたんですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}feeling the sheer power of the art her father creates.
