Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.20,0:35:31.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}もう子供だから純粋だし{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}when the scene transitioned back to her painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.69,0:35:34.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I was able to perform it all in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.50,0:35:35.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}もう全部見えるものが新しくってキラキラ輝いてて{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It was a huge moment for me personally
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.01,0:35:38.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}to go into that painting scene
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.80,0:26:50.37,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そんな世界の中に 、お父さんがいて{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}while still embracing that sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.89,0:26:51.39,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、そのお父さんが{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and the scenery she saw with her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.53,0:35:44.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}She was finally able to say
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.30,0:35:44.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}もっともっとエナにとってすごい人っていう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}that painting is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.33,0:35:48.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}She's still in the middle of her journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.06,0:26:55.13,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}憧れの人 、すごいものを生み出す人っていう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but she finally made it to this point.
