Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.99,0:36:26.49,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、泣きそうっていうのもあるからああ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and since I'm also in the world of art
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.81,0:36:29.31,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、やばいはい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2} where there are no right answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.85,0:36:59.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I really understand how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.90,0:36:32.93,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あの本当台本見た時にめっちゃ泣いちゃったんですよ 、家で{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But it's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.41,0:36:33.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 もう良かったね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Seeing all of Ena's hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.26,0:36:33.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、と思って{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}finally start to pay off...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.97,0:37:07.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Well, "pay off" is a simple way to put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.50,0:37:08.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}うわあ 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but it was just so moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.56,0:37:09.23,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}放送事故{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'm sorry, I'm getting emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.23,0:37:10.05,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Let's move on before I lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.05,0:37:10.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.80,0:36:36.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ね 、5年間{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Ena has really grown,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.40,0:36:37.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ま 、絵奈の時空の中で5年じゃないですけど本当にいろんな思いがあると思うし{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and seeing her find joy in art again
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.23,0:36:39.73,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、皆さんも結構絵奈のストーリーって共感しやすいと思うんですけど私もやっぱり芸術っていうあの正解のないあの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}was such a beautiful moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.51,0:36:46.01,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、世界にいるからこそすごく気持ちが分かるの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I hope you all felt that too
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.98,0:37:34.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}while reading the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:38.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}でもそれだけじゃなくて絵奈が頑張ってきたなんか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It really was
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.88,0:36:51.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ものがちょっとこう報われるというか 、報われるって言ったら簡単なんですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}a wonderful event.
Comment: 0,0:36:51.88,0:36:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.88,0:36:52.59,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、ありがとうございます{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.71,0:37:47.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.12,0:36:54.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ああ 、でもそれが嬉しくて台本初めて読んだ時は自分でも自分の鈴木のおめでとうって気持ちで泣けたし読んでる時はもう絵奈のああ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Ah, but I was so happy that when I first read the script, I cried as Suzuki, thinking, "Congratulations!" And while reading it, I felt Ena's relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.13,0:37:01.63,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、やっとここまで来れたなんかシンプルな気持ちなれたっていうその頑張ってきた張り詰めていたものが1つ解けるみたいなああ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It was like, "I finally made it this far." It was such a simple feeling, like all the tension from working so hard was finally unraveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.41,0:37:08.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、すいません{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.02,0:37:08.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ティッシュいっぱいここにある{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I have plenty of tissues right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.91,0:38:17.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.64,0:37:09.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そう 、なんかそんな思いを込めて自然と涙流しながらで{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yeah, I put those feelings into it and the tears just came naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.67,0:37:12.17,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、やっぱ言葉が詰まる部分とかもあったんですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}There were moments where my words got stuck,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.75,0:37:13.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、やっぱそれがお芝居だし{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but that's what acting is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.43,0:37:14.11,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、本当に絵奈を演じてることのなんかそこの良さをちゃんと私が泣いてたら{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I really felt the beauty of playing Ena. When I was crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.40,0:38:39.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、絵奈として泣いてたら絵も泣いてくれてるしあの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}when I was crying as Ena, she was crying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.84,0:37:21.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}私の間に合わせて 、もちろんセリフもはボタンで押すから次に進むんですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}They matched my timing. Of course, the dialogue moves forward when you press the button,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.31,0:37:23.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、そのボタン押されるまでの間は本当全部切らないで大切にやってくださってるしもう感謝感激みたいな感じでで{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but they didn't cut anything and treated the pauses until the button was pressed with such care. I'm just so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.39,0:37:28.89,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、今回の感想をすごくめちゃくちゃいいストーリーだったって言ってもらえることがたくさんあってなんかしかもその鈴木さんのお芝居がこうで{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I've received so many comments saying this was a fantastic story. And it wasn't just about "Suzuki's acting was like this"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:35.21,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、鈴木さんのこの声がこうでとかじゃなくて{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}or "Suzuki's voice was like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.83,0:37:36.33,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、私じゃなくてちゃんと絵奈の生き様を皆さんが受け止めてくださってなんか喜んでくださって背中を押されてる方とか一緒に頑張ろうって思ったりとか単純に絵奈をずっと応援してくれていた方がもうお{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Instead of focusing on me, everyone really accepted Ena's way of life. People were happy for her, felt encouraged, or decided to work hard alongside her. Those who have been supporting Ena all this time were like,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.71,0:37:46.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、良かったね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"I'm so glad for her!"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.32,0:37:46.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、でもこれからだけどって{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"But this is just the beginning."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.88,0:37:47.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、こう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.54,0:37:47.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかこう 、いろんな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}all these different...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.78,0:37:48.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、こう 、絵奈に対して感情を寄せてくださったことっていうのがすごく嬉しくてあのめっちゃ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}emotions were being directed toward Ena, and that made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.89,0:37:52.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.56,0:37:53.06,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、私も今の私の全力を今の絵奈に注いで演じたので良かったなって感じでございます{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I poured my absolute best into Ena right now, so I'm glad it turned out this way."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.93,0:39:54.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.56,0:39:55.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そうですね 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.46,0:39:56.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ええ 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:39:56.56,0:37:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,=== Corner: Card Illustrations ===
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.56,0:37:59.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}じゃあ 、イラスト見ていきましょう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Now, let's take a look at the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.09,0:37:59.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 あ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.28,0:37:59.78,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、ちなみに絵に向き合い続けて好きなもののせいで苦しみ続けた絵奈に少し希望が見えた瞬間だからって言って私は選んでいたそうです{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}by the way, I chose this scene because it's the moment where a glimmer of hope appears for Ena, who has kept facing her art and suffering because of the thing she loves."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.39,0:40:07.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.08,0:40:07.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}はい 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.96,0:38:06.29,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ではサクッと4分ぐらいでえ 、カードイラストの方も一緒に見ていければなと思います{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Now, let's take a quick four minutes or so to look at the card illustrations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.65,0:40:15.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.26,0:38:08.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}イラスト見る前に 、なんとイラスト制作チームの方から衣装についてのコメントをいただいているのでご紹介します{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Before we look at the art, I actually have some comments from the illustration team regarding the outfits to share with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.04,0:40:22.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.80,0:38:12.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}え 、今回は絵奈が美大にえ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So, this time, the story centers on Ena's struggle to get into art school,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.26,0:38:12.97,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、進むために奮闘したうえで希望レベルに届かず挫折しかけ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}where she almost gives up after failing to reach the level she hoped for,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.71,0:38:17.21,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、それでも諦めないというストーリーをテーマの軸にし{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but ultimately decides not to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.29,0:38:18.79,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、絵描き用エプロンかける制服というモチーフで制作しており{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}The motif for the outfits is "painter's apron over school uniform,"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.29,0:38:20.79,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、絵奈の受験生としてのスタイルをイメージしたデザインにしています{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}designed to capture Ena's style as a student preparing for entrance exams."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.85,0:40:45.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:38:24.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}絵描きスタイルとして既存衣装でもエプロンがありますが 、本イベント衣装は絵奈だけは継ぎ接ぎのエプロンにすることで{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}While she has other apron outfits, only Ena's apron in this event is patched up
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.89,0:38:26.39,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、何度も挫折しかけながらも貫いていく姿を表すなど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}to represent how she keeps pushing forward despite nearly breaking many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.07,0:38:28.57,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、今回ならではのアレンジを効かせたデザインにしています{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's a unique design choice specifically for this event."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.57,0:41:00.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.14,0:38:30.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}また 、セーラー襟やプリーツなどを制服としてのインパクトの強い要素を残しつつ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}They also kept strong uniform elements like the sailor collar and pleats
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:33.13,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、形状アレンジを入れ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}while adding stylistic arrangements
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.13,0:38:33.67,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、衣装感を強めるように意識しております{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}to give it a more distinct "costume" feel."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.27,0:41:09.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.90,0:38:35.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ということで 、イラストこちらになっておりますね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And here is the illustration itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.19,0:41:13.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:38:37.57,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}え 、あと特訓前{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Also, the pre-training art...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.57,0:38:38.15,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、こちらも皆さんすごい反響ね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}everyone gave such a huge reaction to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.07,0:38:39.57,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、くださってね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}She looks like she's having fun painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.17,0:38:40.67,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、楽しんで描いている{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.93,0:41:22.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.48,0:41:23.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}手が汚れている{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Her hands are all dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.16,0:41:24.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.24,0:41:24.91,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}とっても素敵{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.91,0:41:25.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.90,0:38:43.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そして 、そして今回絵奈を見守ってくれて応援してくれた皆様の素敵な特訓前とこれ特訓前と特訓後でございました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And here are the pre-training and post-training versions of everyone who watched over and supported Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.53,0:41:37.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.32,0:38:49.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ね 、奏ではやっぱり{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}You know, Kanade is also
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.24,0:38:50.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの 、創作をしている側の人間なので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}someone on the creative side,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.13,0:38:51.73,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ジャンルは違えど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so even if the genre is different,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.73,0:38:52.33,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、絵奈の気持ちを理解してくれてそして廻人さん{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}she understands Ena's feelings. And Enato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.45,0:38:54.51,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、うん 、廻人さんもすごいね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yeah, Enato-san was amazing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.51,0:38:55.13,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、大切な言葉を絵奈にたくさんかけてくださってあの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}He said so many important things to Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.99,0:38:57.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、みんなでね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}They all
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.68,0:38:58.67,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、アイス食べたりもしてるんで 、よかったら見てくださいってことでヨーグルトのアイスっていうのを思いにしてます{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}eat ice cream together, so please check that out. I chose yogurt-flavored ice cream for that scene.
