Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.62,0:42:05.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}お前かいっていうね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Talk about self-indulgence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.65,0:42:06.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 そしてミクさんね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And then there's Miku.
