Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.58,0:42:08.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}かわいい 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.40,0:39:05.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}素敵 、絵がいっぱい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It's lovely, there are so many drawings.
