Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.37,0:42:14.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.40,0:42:15.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}かわいいね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.00,0:42:15.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
