Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.84,0:42:22.51,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 はい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.51,0:42:23.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
