Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.44,0:42:26.94,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ありがとうございます{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.36,0:42:29.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.04,0:39:15.51,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ということで 、特訓前と特訓後のイラストご覧{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So, those were the pre and post-training illustra—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.85,0:39:17.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、いっ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.42,0:39:17.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、もう 、やだ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.70,0:39:18.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、何回やんの 、これ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}How many times am I going to mess this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.17,0:39:18.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 はい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.30,0:39:18.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、読んでいただきました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}you've seen them all now."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.93,0:42:38.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.92,0:39:20.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}いやあの 、ちょっとストーリーの話もうあと数分できるのでするんですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I have a few more minutes to talk about the story, so I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.17,0:39:22.67,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんか前回のそのお話は{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Regarding the previous story,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.99,0:39:24.49,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ま{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}well,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.68,0:42:49.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}um,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.96,0:42:50.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんでしょうね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.05,0:42:52.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Comment: 0,0:42:52.58,0:39:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.58,0:39:27.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}絵奈 、絵に関するお話じゃなかったんですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}This isn't exactly about Ena's art, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.00,0:39:27.59,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、その1個前のあの私は雨っていう楽曲も歌わせていただいた{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Before this, I also sang the song "I am Rain.""
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.57,0:39:31.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの 、絵奈のお絵お描きって言い方やだな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Back when we were doing the story about Ena's art—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.31,0:39:33.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの 、絵のお話の時は{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I don't really like saying "Ena's drawings."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.89,0:39:34.39,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あのなんかたまたま美術館に行ったんですよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Anyway, I happened to visit an art museum around then.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.10,0:43:12.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:39:40.09,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}それで絵を見るっていうのは何かっていうのを自分もこう踏まえて演じることができて 、絵奈のことを知れて{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I was able to act while reflecting on what it means to look at art, and I got to know Ena better.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.09,0:39:41.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、で 、今回はたまたま道をこう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And this time, I just happened to be
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.14,0:39:41.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ふんふんふんって歩いてたら{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}walking down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.84,0:39:42.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、こう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and there it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.40,0:39:43.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、絵奈が通ってるみたいな 、その{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It was like the place Ena attends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.38,0:39:43.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、多分美術の道をを目指す人が通う学校が{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}A school for people aiming for a career in art
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.01,0:39:45.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、その 、道にあって{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}was right there on that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.82,0:39:46.25,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あ 、こんな感じなんだ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I thought, "Oh, so this is what it's like."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.25,0:39:46.75,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、と思ってそこで傍から見るだけでも{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Even just looking from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.69,0:39:48.19,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかすごい緊張感を感じてすごく厳しいところでやっているんだなっていうの改めて感じながらの収録をさせていただきました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I felt this intense tension and realized she's working in a very strict environment, which I kept in mind during the recording."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.73,0:43:46.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.30,0:39:53.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんかね 、こう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I try to act every day
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.48,0:39:53.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、ちょっとでも皆さんに絵奈のいる場所の質感だったりとかを伝えられたらなと思って日々演じております{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}with the hope of conveying even a little bit of the atmosphere of the world Ena lives in."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.95,0:43:57.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.58,0:43:58.26,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}ありがとうございます{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.26,0:39:59.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 はい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.46,0:39:59.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ということでしてえまだあと数十秒ある{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}it looks like we still have a few dozen seconds left.
