Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.89,0:40:11.39,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ちゃんと覚悟を決められた絵奈の{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but I hope her expression
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.11,0:40:12.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and her singing voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.68,0:40:13.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、表情だったりとか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}which show she's truly made up her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.18,0:40:13.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}are reaching all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.70,0:40:14.20,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、歌声だったりとかが今絶賛届いている最中だったら嬉しいなと思っております{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}right at this very moment."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.77,0:44:34.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.58,0:44:35.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}はい 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.64,0:44:36.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ね 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.80,0:40:19.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}いや 、いいストーリーですよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Man, it's such a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.14,0:40:19.69,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、絵奈は{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Ena is...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.33,0:44:40.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.02,0:40:21.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}愛されていますよ 、こんな素敵なお話いただけて{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}She's so loved, getting a wonderful story like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.09,0:44:43.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.60,0:40:22.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ということで 、え{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And with that...
Comment: 0,0:40:22.32,0:40:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,=== Corner: Song Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.32,0:40:22.82,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、今回のイベントとのために描き下ろしていただいた3DMVを見てから楽曲についてお話ししていこうと思います{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'd like to talk about the music after we watch the 3DMV"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.64,0:44:50.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}that was specially written for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.14,0:44:50.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}それではどうぞ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.49,0:44:51.99,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.88,0:45:11.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}何者にもなれない体と借りた命の中で息をして{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Breathing inside a borrowed life and a body that can't become anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.04,0:45:21.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}奥の方まで深く潜れば今もあの日の自分が{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}if I dive deep into the depths, the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.12,0:45:21.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}まだ笑ってる{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}is still smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.75,0:45:32.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.20,0:45:32.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}振り返れば確かに残る{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}If I look back, they certainly remain—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.13,0:45:42.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.28,0:45:42.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}胸に芽生えていた夢のかけら{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}the fragments of dreams that sprouted in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.72,0:45:47.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.40,0:45:47.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}理想の影に押しつぶされてそれはいつしか嫌いに変わってしまった過去を嘆いてみても仕方がないよな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Crushed by the shadow of ideals, it eventually turned into hatred. Even if I regret the past, it can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.93,0:46:09.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.58,0:46:10.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ほんの小さな優しい光{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}A tiny, gentle light...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.95,0:46:14.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.72,0:46:15.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}信じた思いはまた届かない{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}The feelings I believed in still don't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.41,0:46:20.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.24,0:46:20.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}それでも乾いたまま目の前にある真っ白な景色にこの手でもっと未来を描いてみたい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Even so, I want to draw more of the future with these hands on the pure white scenery that remains dry before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.05,0:46:33.55,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.00,0:46:41.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}たとえきれいじゃなくても{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Even if it's not beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.24,0:46:44.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}自分らしく{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I want to keep drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.24,0:46:49.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ただ目に映る{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}this world as it appears to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.76,0:46:50.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}この世界を描いていたい{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.37,0:46:59.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.16,0:41:31.87,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ということで 、すいません{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And there we go. Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.87,0:41:32.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、私の画面が{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}my screen just... excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.43,0:41:32.99,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、失礼します{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.95,0:47:06.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.54,0:47:07.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}今回のイベントのためにちょちょPさんに描き下ろしていただいたその絵の名前はタイトル初解禁ですね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}That was the 3DMV for the song written by Chochop-san for this event. This is the first time the title has been revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.43,0:47:16.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.48,0:47:16.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}その絵の名前はですよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}The name of the song is "Sono E no Namae wa" (The Name of That Painting).
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.79,0:47:19.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 3DMVでございました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.63,0:47:21.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.30,0:47:22.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}え{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.00,0:41:42.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}先にえ 、あ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}first... oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.92,0:41:43.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、いいのか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.47,0:47:27.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.54,0:41:46.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}自分のメモがちょちょPさんのコメントかと思って衣装 、あれってなって{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I thought my notes were Chochop-san's comments, and I was like, "Wait, the outfit?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.48,0:41:46.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、違いました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But I was wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.31,0:41:46.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 これ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}This is actually
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.80,0:41:47.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、私の私が事前にスタッフさんに送っていたメモじゃ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2} the memo I sent to the staff beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.11,0:41:49.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、さ 、読みますね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Let me read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.57,0:47:40.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.22,0:41:50.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}え 、聞くだけで絵奈の道のりを感じることができて泣けてきます{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"Just listening to it makes me feel Ena's journey, and it brings me to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.69,0:47:46.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.38,0:41:55.65,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}タイトルに絵と奈と彼女の名前が入っていて 、まさに絵奈を描いた楽曲だと感じました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}The title contains the kanji for 'E' and 'Na' from her name, so I felt it was truly a song that depicts Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.57,0:47:54.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.34,0:41:58.47,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}後悔も悔しい気持ちも 、苦しい気持ちもただ光するのではなく{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Instead of just letting the regret, frustration, and pain be, I sang with the resolve to turn them into strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.65,0:42:00.15,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、力に変えていこうとする覚悟とその覚悟ができた彼女の前向きな気持ちを込めて歌いました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and with the positive feelings she found once she made that decision.""
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.55,0:48:08.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.08,0:42:04.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}と 、過去の私はスタッフさんにメールしております{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}That's what the past version of me emailed to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.61,0:48:11.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.84,0:42:07.29,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ちょちょPさんのコメントはですね 、プロセカ放送局とかでご紹介してるので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}As for Chochop-san's comments, they've been shared on the ProSeka Broadcasting Station
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.93,0:42:08.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あとTwitter{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and on Twitter—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.50,0:42:09.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、Twitter 、Xでもあると思うのでご覧ください{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}well, X—so please check them out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.00,0:48:20.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.56,0:42:11.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}そうですね 、そんな思いを込めて歌いました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But yeah, those were the feelings I put into the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.93,0:48:24.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.54,0:42:15.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あの過去を振り返っているように感じられる歌詞もあるんですけど 、ま{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}There are lyrics that feel like she's looking back at the past, but
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.64,0:42:16.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、でもなんかこう 、本当に今の絵奈が振り返っている{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}it feels like the current Ena is the one doing the reflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.67,0:48:35.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.38,0:42:20.11,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}だからなんか多分絵奈は後悔も絶対してるけど 、でもそれがあったから今があるってちゃんと分かってる子だと思うんで{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I think Ena definitely has regrets, but she's the kind of girl who understands that she is who she is now because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.81,0:42:22.31,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、もう過去を振り返るフレーズも過去の絵奈みたいになんかこう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So, even for the phrases about the past, I didn't want to sing them with total agony like the old Ena would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.04,0:48:57.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、苦しさ全開で歌いたくなくてあのそれを意識して歌ったりとか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I was very conscious of that while recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.44,0:42:30.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}自分の覚悟が決まった 、その{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I sang with that sense of resolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.88,0:42:31.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、さっきも言ったんですけど 、ストーリーの方で{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}and like I mentioned during the story discussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.72,0:42:32.23,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかその安心感とやっと分かった明るい気持ちを込めて歌いつつも{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}with that sense of relief and the newfound brightness she finally found.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.03,0:42:35.53,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、でもこれがまたゴールじゃないので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But this isn't the goal yet;
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.44,0:49:15.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、スタートなので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}it's a new start.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.40,0:42:39.57,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ちゃんとそのあい 、真ん中の気持ちみたいなね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I tried to capture that middle ground of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.23,0:42:40.73,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかそこを意識して歌いました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}while I was singing."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.02,0:49:24.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.52,0:42:42.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なので 、こう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So, rather than one big explosion of emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.56,0:42:43.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、大きな感情がドーンってありかは本当に静かに自分の中でふつふつと言葉を奏でて鼓舞してる{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}it's more like quietly simmering the words inside and encouraging herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.09,0:49:36.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.68,0:42:49.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}自分をね 、頑張ろうって胸を自分で叩くというね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Like she's patting her own chest to say, "I can do this."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.83,0:42:50.33,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、鼓舞するっていうのを意識して歌わせていただきました{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I sang it with that kind of self-encouragement in mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.76,0:49:46.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.26,0:42:53.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんか 、やっぱ泣いちゃうんだよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Man, it really does make me cry.
Comment: 0,0:49:48.21,0:49:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.21,0:49:49.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.10,0:42:55.30,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}フル聞けるんです 歌った人だから{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I get to hear the full version because I'm the one who sang it."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.30,0:42:55.83,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、私{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.27,0:49:50.77,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.83,0:49:53.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.50,0:49:54.07,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ごめんなさいね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.07,0:49:54.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.66,0:42:57.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}あの 、泣いちゃうのよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'm just going to end up crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.35,0:49:57.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.00,0:42:59.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんかもう 、だめなのよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I just can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.21,0:49:58.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.76,0:43:00.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんかもう 、このストーリーも歌も泣いちゃうのよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Both the story and the song make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.49,0:50:02.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.02,0:43:01.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}どうしちゃおう 、どうしましょうね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}What am I going to do? What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.23,0:43:02.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。 この話を{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}About this story...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.16,0:43:02.75,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、今回も泣かないと思ったんですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I thought I wouldn't cry this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.75,0:43:03.35,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、泣いちゃったしさ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but I ended up crying anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.09,0:50:07.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.74,0:50:08.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ね 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.72,0:43:04.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ということで 、あ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Anyway, oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.94,0:43:05.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、フル聞けるって言った私にちょっと嫉妬したそこのあなた{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}to those of you who were a little jealous that I get to hear the full version,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.49,0:43:06.99,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、大丈夫です{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}don't worry."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.71,0:50:15.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.38,0:43:08.31,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}え 、今回の描き下ろし楽曲{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}The 2DMV for this event's new song,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.31,0:43:08.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、その絵の名前はの2DMVもこの後22時15分にプロセカ公式YouTubeにアップされますので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"The Name of That Painting," will be uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel at 10:15 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.33,0:43:13.83,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、3DMVとともにぜひそちらもチェックしてください{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}So please check that out along with the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.64,0:50:31.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.56,0:43:16.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}だからきっとフル聞けるってことですよね 、2DMV{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}That means you'll be able to hear the full version in the 2DMV,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.90,0:43:17.53,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、今まで通りであれば{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}if it's like it has been until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.15,0:50:36.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.84,0:50:37.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ね 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.78,0:50:38.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}2DMV私もまだ見てないんですよ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I haven't seen the 2DMV yet myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.03,0:50:40.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.58,0:43:20.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}で 、あ{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And, oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.70,0:43:21.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、じゃあ 、3DMVのちょっと感想をね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Let me share some thoughts on the 3DMV,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.50,0:43:22.25,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、今更ですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}even if it's a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.25,0:43:22.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、言うとなんか元々フルで撮ってはいるけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}We record the full song, but the parts are divided up,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.87,0:43:25.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、歌い分けはしているので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.60,0:43:26.33,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、どこが絵奈パートになるかって{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}which parts would be Ena's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.73,0:50:54.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.38,0:43:27.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}で 、歌い出しが{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Since the song starts
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.66,0:43:28.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの 、2号の3人から順に始まるので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}with the other three Niigo members in order,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.27,0:43:29.77,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんか脳内の3DMV{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}in the 3DMV in my head—
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.31,0:43:30.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、私の妄想3DMVはあ絵奈じゃない{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}well, my imaginary version of the song—
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.95,0:43:33.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、歌{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.50,0:43:34.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかこうなんだろう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}"How is this going to start?"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.04,0:43:34.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、どうやって始まるんだろう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I wondered if
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.74,0:43:35.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、と思って 、4人とか5人がこう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}all four or five of them would suddenly appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.48,0:43:36.03,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、パッと映るのかこう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}or if it would start
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.59,0:43:37.09,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、歌い出しの瑞希から始まるのか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}with Mizuki, who sings the first line.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.75,0:43:38.25,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、と思っていたらなんかこう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.85,0:43:39.35,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、絵奈がずっと映っていて{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Ena was on screen the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.87,0:43:40.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.52,0:43:41.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、もちろんその分ね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.10,0:43:41.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'm happy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.70,0:43:42.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、他のキャラクターを応援してくれてる方はその時はまたその子の映っているパーセンテージが高いと鈴木も嬉しいですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}when other characters get a high percentage of screen time for their fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.83,0:43:46.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、でもなんかこう{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but this MV
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.50,0:43:47.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、絵奈へのスポットがすごく多いMVで{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}really put the spotlight on Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.71,0:43:48.21,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかそれがすごくストーリーとマッチしていてなんか絵奈の生き様を映してくれているMVだな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}It matched the story so well and really captured Ena's way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.17,0:43:52.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、と思って{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.68,0:43:53.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、すごく 、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}as her voice actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.18,0:43:53.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、演者側として嬉しかった{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}it made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.81,0:43:54.45,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、っていうのがありましたね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}That's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.83,0:51:51.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.72,0:43:56.97,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}絵が映ってるっていうのも 、毎回そうなですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Her drawings being shown is always the case, but
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.97,0:43:57.49,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、その絵奈のストーリーの時の楽曲がはなんか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}the songs for Ena's stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.35,0:44:00.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ま 、ちょっと場所もなんかちょっとずつ地上に上がってる感じもあるし{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}well, the location feels like it's gradually rising toward the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.71,0:44:02.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかそれも{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}And that,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.34,0:44:03.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ま 、これはただのオタクの考察ですけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}well, this is just my own geeky analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.16,0:44:03.75,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、なんかそういうのも嬉しかったりとか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}but things like that make me happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.44,0:52:08.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.94,0:44:04.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}でも 、まだそんな数回{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}But I've only seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.92,0:44:05.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、私も数回しか見れてないので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}a few times so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.54,0:44:06.17,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、じっくり見たいなと思います{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}so I want to watch it more closely."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.70,0:52:15.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.20,0:44:08.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ちょ 、2DMV楽しみすぎますね{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Man, I'm so excited for the 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.17,0:52:17.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.74,0:52:18.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}はい 。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.84,0:52:19.47,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}かな{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.47,0:52:20.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}...
Comment: 0,0:52:20.12,0:44:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.12,0:44:11.63,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}なんか言い残したことないな 、ないと思いますけど{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I don't think I have anything left to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.63,0:44:12.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ま 、でも全部もう本当に絵奈の声に{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Well, I've really put everything
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.67,0:44:14.35,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、私は絵奈にかけて押しているので{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}into Ena's voice, so I'm rooting for her."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.35,0:44:15.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、ぜひぜひ 、何よりも絵奈の生き様を楽曲とストーリーで感じていただければなと思います{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}More than anything, I hope you can feel Ena's way of life through the song and the story.
