Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.96,0:44:19.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}ね 、これからも絵奈を応援してください{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}Please continue to support Ena,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.81,0:44:20.49,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、皆様{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.13,0:52:41.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}。{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.66,0:52:42.16,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}絵奈を応援してくださってる方本当にありがとうございます{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}To those who already support her, thank you so much."
