Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.42,0:44:39.99,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}配信をご覧の皆さん 、いかがでしたでしょうか{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}To everyone watching the stream, how was it?
