Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.48,0:54:06.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,{\\fs24\\a6}、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.30,0:54:06.96,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"{\\fs24\\a6}、また私は 、あの{\\N}{\\fs48\\a2}I'll be watching it once I close this screen,"
